description: Try our easy to follow Beef & Vegetable Stir-fry recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Stir-fry,Quick & easy dinner,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Seafood free,Wheat free,Egg free,Low sugar,Beef
name: Beef & Vegetable Stir-fry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat a wok over a high heat until very hot. Add sesame seeds and shake wok over the heat for about 2 mins until toasted. Remove to a bowl. Return wok to heat.
Add 1 tsp of the oil to the wok and swirl to coat. Add 1/4 of the beef. Sear on high heat for 1 minute or until browned. Remove from wok, reheat and repeat with remaining beef.

Add remaining oil to wok with vegetables. Toss for 1 minute. Add 1 tbs water, cover and cook for 1 minute. Remove cover. Return beef to wok with hoisin sauce and sesame seeds. Toss through to heat and serve with steamed rice.
